tags: even if this isn't your song
where do you think you're going?
summary: This song is to beautiful and delicate, it made me think of me for some reason. I think I'm losing myself to some uncertain...
body:
This song is to beautiful and delicate, it made me think of me for some reason. I think I’m losing myself to some uncertain destination of my heart and to a lot of insecurity.

I know I have to act positively and act on my life and what’s happening, and that happiness starts from me, but right now I just can’t. I can’t feel it and I don’t know if I ever will. I’m still climbing up again after one of the lowest periods of my life and my family and friends make it all better but.. there’s always a part of me that’s somehow afraid of being fully happy.

I have to remember that my past self it’s still here and that I’m gonna be the best version of myself.

I don’t know my identity and I’m struggling with that, but as long as songs and music are still here (and Taylor and her words too), i feel safe and i know that i can do it. I can find happiness.

And whether people want it or not, I’m on the right path and I’m gonna create my future.
